name: XX1 - E.T. "MOXXAPHA"
description:
First contact occurred in year 2024 on their very own space vessel near Luna.

We managed to communicate with one of them who turned out to be their leader.
They call themselves "Moxxapha" but we prefer to call them "Methuselah" because it turns out their existence existed before humans were born.

From the contact we can conclude that they are from an exoplanet believed to be about 12.7 billion years old "PSR B1620−26 b" with the unofficial nickname "the Genesis planet".

Their possession of FTL (Faster than Light) travel technology signifies that they are far more advanced than us, but they didn't show any hostility against us since the first contact.

Are their existence a threat to humanity? I hope it's not.

Cpt. Abraham C. Easley
March 14, 2025
